# Archive Folder Structure

Location: `/archive/`

## Public Folder

- **/Public/Exhibits** â€” PDF-A format with Bates numbering
- **/Public/Index** â€” CSV and JSON indexes
- **/Public/Summaries** â€” 2-pagers and FAQs

## Restricted Folder

- **/Restricted/Unredacted** â€” Access-controlled sensitive materials
- **/Restricted/Legal_Work_Product** â€” Attorney work product

## Press Kit Folder

- **/Press_Kit/OnePager.pdf** â€” 1-page case summary
- **/Press_Kit/Timeline.png** â€” Visual timeline
- **/Press_Kit/Top10_Exhibits.pdf** â€” Key evidence highlights

---

# Case Archive Subfolders

Location: `/archive/Case_Archive/`

- **00_Timeline/** â€” Timeline.csv with key dates
- **01_Pleadings/** â€” All filed pleadings
- **02_Exhibits/** â€” Bates-numbered exhibits (Bates_0001-000N)
- **03_Orders/** â€” Court orders and judgments
- **04_Notices/** â€” Notices of filing and service
- **05_FOIA/** â€” FOIA requests and responses

---

# File Naming Conventions

<aside>
**Best Practices:**
Date-stamp all files: YYYY-MM-DD_Document-Name_v#.pdf
Keep consistent slugs for easy searching
Include version numbers for drafts
Export final versions as PDF-A for permanence

</aside>

---

# Quick Setup Checklist

- [ ]  Create root folders: briefs, appendix, addendum, oa, orders, kits, release, archive
- [ ]  Create root files: index.html, Master_Index.csv, Start_Here.html, CHECKSUMS.txt, [CHANGELOG.md](http://CHANGELOG.md)
- [ ]  Set up /archive/ with Public, Restricted, Press_Kit subfolders
- [ ]  Create Case_Archive with 00â€“05 numbered folders
- [ ]  Seed Timeline.csv with 5 key dates
- [ ]  Add initial [CHANGELOG.md](http://CHANGELOG.md) entry
- [ ]  Set permissions: Public = read-only, Restricted = access-controlled

<aside>
**Purpose:** This structure makes collaboration scalable, ensures portability, and maintains verifiability across all filings and appeals.

</aside>